title: Adele's all smiles as she arrives in Sydney ahead of Australian/New Zealand tour
text:
Adele's all smiles as she arrives in Sydney ahead of Australian/New Zealand tour Last updated 13:14, February 20 2017 Breakfast 
The superstar laughed with ground crew as she arrived on a private jet ahead of her first show. 
Adele greeted Sydney with smiles when her private jet touched down on Sunday night. 
The Hello singer is in Australia for her six night tour, before heading our way to play three nights in Auckland at Mt Smart Stadium. 
She arrived late, and was seen carrying her 4-year-old son, Angelo, from the plane wrapped in a blanket. MARIO ANZUONI/REUTERS 
Singer Adele arrives at the 59th Annual Grammy Awards in Los Angeles. 
TV 1 had footage of her big grin for the boy when they arrived.
